<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="O" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Officious" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Officious,</orth> ready to do service, busy: <cit><quote>be every one o. to make this banquet,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 5.2.202" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. V, 2, 202</bibl></cit>. In a bad sense, == obtruding one's service, meddling: <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.2.330" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 2, 330</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 2.3.159" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 3, 159</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.871" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 871</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.237" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 237</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 1.8.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 8, 14</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>